# iCloud Drive sometimes creates "filename 2.ext" duplicates when files
# are modified during a sync. Ignore the pattern so they never get
# committed by accident. Real files in this repo do not use " 2." suffixes.
* 2.html
* 2.webp
* 2.png
* 2.jpg
* 2.xml
* 2.css
* 2.js
* 2.mjs
* 3.html
